title: U.S. And Russia Sign Deal to Minimize Air Risks in Syria
text:
U.S. And Russia Sign Deal to Minimize Air Risks in Syria 
Published By: Time - Today 
U.S. officials said it was a narrow arrangement that does not lessen Washington's concern about the Russian military campaign in Syria...
